{"tid":881312,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街啦痾血添","createTime":"2018-10-29T10:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T04:41:42.000Z","uid":133581,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d3d9a93b26b1a0644ef7d9abe004650e74891907","tid":881312,"uid":133581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:53:10.000Z","msg":"前幾日痾屎個時有少少血咁<br />\n不過我個時以為因為抿得太大力損左無理到<br />\n結果琴晚久違咁跑完步番到 發現痾完有d血係度 係明顯見到血紅色<br />\n我嚇撚到仆街 即刻上網search 好似話有血紅色係長期便秘 壓力大咁所以有痔瘡 但有種叫隱性便血 都有可能會痾血 黑便咁 嚴重既可能係cancer <br />\n<br />\nreference <a href=\"http://www.union.org/new/tc_chi/health_info/health_articles_gi5.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.union.org%2Fnew%2Ftc_chi%2Fhealth_info%2Fhealth_articles_gi5.htm&d=MzqCjGERpgcm%2BCiWhigIoviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=22e0e5b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.union.org/new/tc_chi/health_info/health_articles_gi5.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n我而家就係黑便加血 唔知係咪最近壓力大 同埋無乜食菜 聽日打去St Teresa 做個basic check 而家好撚驚 有無巴打試過 我求個安心 唔想咁快刷首抽住"},{"pid":"10831f06e9a99260bd00fb9f3a7c431d3c886791","tid":881312,"uid":94370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:54:48.000Z","msg":"呢啲環境只有大腸同巨龍二揀一"},{"pid":"acc79a2ddd8246a54e8f760a6b22d8f1b9d4c7c9","tid":881312,"uid":67806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:54:57.000Z","msg":"好彩你無圖，RIP"},{"pid":"779a5aef941f5e929b63eb1766fd5849ed49674b","tid":881312,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:55:46.000Z","msg":"要俾醫生爆菊了"},{"pid":"593d6307f5969231fc13915382393c5c622dea96","tid":881312,"uid":133581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"779a5aef941f5e929b63eb1766fd5849ed49674b","tid":881312,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:55:46.000Z","msg":"要俾醫生爆菊了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:57:21.000Z","msg":"爆菊唔驚 最驚cancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6538e9cf7c98061fe8755743a3e3322